smul:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
theorem is_conformal_map.smul (hf : is_conformal_map f) {c : R} (hc : c ≠ 0) : is_conformal_map («expr • » c f) :=
  by
  rcases hf with ⟨c', hc', li, rfl⟩
  exact ⟨c * c', mul_ne_zero hc hc', li, smul_smul _ _ _⟩
#align is_conformal_map.smul is_conformal_map.smul
ne_zero:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →L[ ] » -/
theorem ne_zero [nontrivial M'] {f' : «expr →L[ ] » M' R N} (hf' : is_conformal_map f') : f' ≠ 0 :=
  by
  rintro rfl
  rcases exists_ne (0 : M') with ⟨a, ha⟩
  exact ha (hf'.injective rfl)
#align ne_zero ne_zero
is_conformal_map_of_subsingleton:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →L[ ] » -/
@[nontriviality]
theorem is_conformal_map_of_subsingleton [subsingleton M] (f' : «expr →L[ ] » M R N) : is_conformal_map f' :=
  ⟨1, one_ne_zero, ⟨0, fun x => by simp [subsingleton.elim x 0]⟩, subsingleton.elim _ _⟩
#align is_conformal_map_of_subsingleton is_conformal_map_of_subsingleton

theorem is_conformal_map_id : is_conformal_map (id R M) :=

is_conformal_map_const_smul:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
theorem is_conformal_map_const_smul (hc : c ≠ 0) : is_conformal_map («expr • » c (id R M)) :=
  is_conformal_map_id.smul hc
#align is_conformal_map_const_smul is_conformal_map_const_smul
is_conformal_map:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →ₗᵢ[ ] » -/
protected theorem linear_isometry.is_conformal_map (f' : «expr →ₗᵢ[ ] » M R N) :
    is_conformal_map f'.to_continuous_linear_map :=
  ⟨1, one_ne_zero, f', (one_smul _ _).symm⟩
#align linear_isometry.is_conformal_map linear_isometry.is_conformal_map
injective:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →L[ ] » -/
protected theorem injective {f : «expr →L[ ] » M' R N} (h : is_conformal_map f) : function.injective f :=
  by
  rcases h with ⟨c, hc, li, rfl⟩
  exact (smul_right_injective _ hc).comp li.injective
#align injective injective
comp:
theorem comp (hg : is_conformal_map g) (hf : is_conformal_map f) : is_conformal_map (g.comp f) :=
  by
  rcases hf with ⟨cf, hcf, lif, rfl⟩
  rcases hg with ⟨cg, hcg, lig, rfl⟩
  refine' ⟨cg * cf, mul_ne_zero hcg hcf, lig.comp lif, _⟩
  rw [smul_comp, comp_smul, mul_smul]
  rfl
#align comp comp
